1979;;A Force of One;;American;;Paul Aaron;;Chuck Norris, Jennifer O'Neill, Clu Gulager;;action;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Force_of_One;;When a team of undercover narcotics officers is targeted by a serial killer, the police recruit karate champion Matt Logan (Chuck Norris) to bring the murders to an end. Narcotics Officer Amanda "Mandy" Rust (Jennifer O'Neill) discovers that a traitor within the police ranks is behind the killings.